{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 8306352}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por Resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xBA; 1.175, de 25 de agosto de 1997, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a de Pesca, del Ministerio de Econom&#xED;a, Fomento y Reconstrucci&#xF3;n, modif&#xED;case el numeral 2&#xBA; de la Resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xBA; 604, de 1986, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, que autoriz&#xF3; a Pesquera San Miguel Ltda., hoy&nbsp; PESQUERA SAN MIGUEL S.A., para ampliar actividades pesqueras con la nave &quot;Westport&quot;, en el sentido de actualizar las caracter&#xED;sticas n&#xE1;uticas de esta &#xFA;ltima, en los t&#xE9;rminos que se indica:</div><br><br><div class=\"p\">Nombre&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;Westport&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">Matr&#xED;cula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2455</div><div class=\"p\">Eslora de arqueo&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  40,9 m.</div><div class=\"p\">T.R.G.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 479,4 t.</div><div class=\"p\">Capacidad de bodega&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 414 m3.</div><div class=\"p\">Arte de pesca&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Cerco</div><br></div>", "i": 8306353}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Valpara&#xED;so, 25 de agosto de 1997.- Juan Manuel Cruz S&#xE1;nchez, Subsecretario de Pesca.</div><br></div>", "i": 8306354}], "proyectos": [], "otrosSistemas": [], "jurisprudencia": [], "doctrina": [], "metadatos": {"tiene_notas": false, "tipos_numeros": [{"tipo": "3", "numero": "1175", "abreviacio